\c 141 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 141\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Yeroo Qoramanii Fi Yeroo Ari'ataman Akka Hin Kufneef Kadhachuu (Faarfannaa Daawit)
\m \bd 1\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, ani sin waammadha, ati ariifadhuu na bira ga'i! Yommuun si waammadhu, gurra keetiin gara sagalee koo dhaggeeffadhu.
\m \bd 2\bd* Kadhanni koo akka ixaana aarfamuutti, harka koo gara keetti ol qabuun koos akka aarsaa galgalaatti si duratti anaaf haa fudhatamu!
\m \bd 3\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, eegduu afaan koo eegu, tiksee saaqamuu hidhii kootii tiksus anaaf dhaabi.
\m \bd 4\bd* Hidhata namoota dabaa hojjetanii ta'ee, jal'inaan waa akkan hin raawwannetti, garaan koo gara wanta hamaatti akka hin jal'anne godhi! Nyaanni isaanii inni namatti tolus anatti haa hafu!
\m \bd 5\bd* Namni qajeelaan na rukutuun anaaf gaarii dha, na ifachuun isaas akka dibata mataa kootii ti; mataan koos kanaan dibamuu hin didu; hojii warra hamaa godhanii irratti garuu, ani amma iyyuu kadhachuu hin dhiisu.
\m \bd 6\bd* Abboonni firdii isaanii kattaa irraa yeroo gad darbataman, wanti ani dubbadhe akka namatti tolu jaratti in dhaga'ama.
\m \bd 7\bd* Akkuma nama lafa qotee garagaggalcheetti, lafeen isaaniis iddoo lafa jalaa dura tatamsa'ee jira.
\m \bd 8\bd* Iji koo garuu gara kee in ilaala, yaa Waaqayyo gooftaa, ani kooluu sitti galeera, ati lubbuu koo hin gatin!
\m \bd 9\bd* Futtaasaa isaan anaaf kaa'an irraa, meendoo warra hamaa hojjetanii irraas na eegi.
\m \bd 10\bd* Ani jalaa nan ba'a, warri jal'oonni immoo kiyyoo isaaniitti haa kufan!
